@timestamp 2026-04-10
@type discovery
@id D6
@subject ag3_loop_state_blocks_simple_once
@finding ag3_loop은 last_write_idx/idle_ticks/tick 인터-iter 상태 보유 → 단순 ONCE 전환 불가. anomaly detection이 wi delta에 의존. 해결책 후보: (1) state persistence file (~/.airgenome/ag3_loop_state.json) (2) self-suicide watchdog after N iters (3) launchd KeepAlive=false + StartInterval로 running하되 코드 내 max-iter exit
@__raw__ {"type":"discovery","id":"D6","subject":"ag3_loop_state_blocks_simple_once","finding":"ag3_loop은 last_write_idx/idle_ticks/tick 인터-iter 상태 보유 → 단순 ONCE 전환 불가. anomaly detection이 wi delta에 의존. 해결책 후보: (1) state persistence file (~/.airgenome/ag3_loop_state.json) (2) self-suicide watchdog after N iters (3) launchd KeepAlive=false + StartInterval로 running하되 코드 내 max-iter exit","timestamp":"2026-04-10"}

