@ts 2026-04-19T12:47:15Z
@type fix
@source airgenome/bin/claudx_abort_root_fix
@action claudx ABORT 근본수정 — expired exhausted purge + empty-pool default fallback 반전
@status shipped
@test_status ran
@related M13_claudx M14_session_defaults CONVERGENCE_REQUIRES_LIVE_EXECUTION
@detail 직전 incident (@ts 2026-04-19T12:31:47Z) 의 drill_tomorrow 항목을 즉시 처리. 근본원인 2개 확정: (1) exhausted.json 에 expired entry 누적 — claude1(until=1776601647, 9분 전 만료)/claude4/"" 가 stale 상태로 pool.loadPool 필터에서 accounts 3개 즉시 축소 → pool.pickBest 가 실효 계정 많아도 빈 결과 반환 빈도 ↑. (2) v2 의 empty-pool ABORT-by-default — CLAUDX_ALLOW_EMPTY=1 수동 우회 요구. 사용자가 두 번이나 이 우회를 타이핑 해야 cl 기동 성공 = 사용성 파괴. 수정 2지점: bin/claudx 진입 초입 (mkdir $CLAUDX_STATE 직후, _loadgate 이전, subcommand case 이전) 에 _prune_exhausted() 함수 추가 — jq --argjson now 로 `with_entries(select(.value.until // 0 | tonumber > $now))` in-place rewrite, 변경 있을 때만 info 로그 1줄. 진입 1회마다 자동 수행 → stale 누적 0. 두번째 수정: empty-pool 분기의 if 조건을 `[ "${CLAUDX_ALLOW_EMPTY:-0}" != "1" ]` 에서 `[ "${CLAUDX_ABORT_ON_EMPTY:-0}" = "1" ] && ...` 로 반전. 기본 동작 = ABORT 대신 info "no acct — using default ~/.claude" 로 fallback (기존 코드 line 241 이미 존재). 엄격 모드 원하면 CLAUDX_ABORT_ON_EMPTY=1 env. 실측 prune (위 수정 파일 배포 직전 Mac exhausted.json 수동 적용): 7 → 4 entries — 남은 것 claude5/12/9/3 (52분 후 reset). pool.js status (prune 후): claude4=ok (week72%/session0%) / claude6=ok (50%/4%) 두 계정 pick 대기. 테스트: 사용자가 Mac 에서 cl 1회 실행 → 기동 성공 확인 ("나는되"). bash -n syntax check pass. 이 entry 가 CONVERGENCE_REQUIRES_LIVE_EXECUTION 원칙 (맨 상단 ossified, 같은 세션에 골화) 의 @test_status=ran 첫 사용례 — 설계/커밋만 아닌 실제 러닝 세션 검증 완료.
@__raw__ {"ts":"2026-04-19T12:47:15Z","type":"fix","source":"airgenome/bin/claudx_abort_root_fix","status":"shipped","test_status":"ran","related":["M13_claudx","M14_session_defaults","CONVERGENCE_REQUIRES_LIVE_EXECUTION"],"root_causes":[{"id":"expired_exhausted_accumulation","evidence":"exhausted.json 7 entries, 3 expired (claude1/claude4/empty-string, until 9-60min past)","impact":"pool.loadPool filter excludes 3 accounts needlessly → pickBest empty more often"},{"id":"empty_pool_abort_by_default","evidence":"v2 required CLAUDX_ALLOW_EMPTY=1 manual bypass","impact":"user hit ABORT twice in one session, cl startup blocked"}],"changes":[{"file":"bin/claudx","site":"after mkdir CLAUDX_STATE, before _loadgate","type":"addition","artifact":"_prune_exhausted() function","logic":"jq with_entries filter by until > now, in-place rewrite, info log only on change"},{"file":"bin/claudx","site":"empty-pool branch (~line 185)","type":"inversion","from":"CLAUDX_ALLOW_EMPTY=1 required to bypass ABORT","to":"CLAUDX_ABORT_ON_EMPTY=1 required to enable ABORT (default=fallback)"}],"live_prune_result":{"before_entries":7,"after_entries":4,"restored_accounts":["claude1","claude4",""],"remaining_exhausted":["claude5","claude12","claude9","claude3"]},"post_prune_pool_status":{"ok":["claude4","claude6"],"retry_at":["claude1","claude2","claude7","claude8","claude10","claude11"],"local_exh":["claude3","claude5","claude9","claude12"]},"verification":{"syntax":"bash -n PASS","user_test":"cl kickoff on Mac succeeded","user_confirmation":"나는되"},"follow_ups":["nexus iOS toml deletion commit","M15 telegram implementation","session_cap=95 threshold tune review (separate track)"]}

@ts 2026-04-21T04:37:00Z
@type feat
@source airgenome/hook-bus-transcript-watcher
@action Claude Code hook 프로토콜 포기 + transcript-watcher로 전환 — .claude/settings.json 파일 0
@status shipped
@test_status ran
@related raw#9 HEXA-ONLY, raw#10 proof-carrying, raw#27 session-interrupt-recovery, stage0 re-entrance deadlock, hexa-lang stdin detachment
@detail airgenome이 Claude Code 공식 hook을 쓰려던 시도 3건이 모두 근본 제약에 걸림 — (1) hexa-lang stage0 wrapper가 `hexa run` 자식 stdin을 /dev/null로 리다이렉트해 read_stdin()이 영구 "". (2) stage0 mkdir-lock이 단일 semaphore라 hook 이벤트가 batch 잡 뒤에 5~10분 대기. (3) 네이티브 `.sh` 래퍼가 raw#9 .sh ban 위반. 해결: Claude Code 공식 hook 포기 → transcript JSONL watch 방식. ~/.claude/projects/<slug>/*.jsonl 파일을 launchd LaunchAgent가 5초마다 폴링, .hook-cursor.json byte offset으로 증분 처리. airgenome/hooks/hook_main.hexa 네이티브 바이너리로 컴파일 (254KB Mach-O arm64), airgenome/bin/airgenome-init 네이티브 바이너리로 LaunchAgent 자동 설치 (.sh wrapper 없음, argv[0]에서 root 유도). hexa-lang/build/hexa_stage0에 HEXA_STAGE0_OWNER 재진입 guard + 30분 etime force-reap 추가. hexa-lang/tool/flatten_imports.hexa에 safe_write_file inline fallback. nexus/shared/harness/safe_hexa_launchd.sh에 env allowlist(HOOK_/AIRGENOME_/CLAUDE_/HEXA_/NEXUS_*) + tail -s 0.1 + cat-fallback. trade-off: observation only, pre_tool 실시간 block 불가 — tool이 transcript에 기록될 시점엔 이미 실행됨. 검증: seed(22 transcripts) + synthetic line inject → 10초 안에 observe/tools 로그 delta 확인 + launchctl list exit=0.
@commits airgenome=8e381933 hexa-lang=93c3c4d3 nexus=3d9dcd3d
@__raw__ {"ts":"2026-04-21T04:37:00Z","type":"feat","source":"airgenome/hook-bus-transcript-watcher","status":"shipped","test_status":"ran","related":["raw#9","raw#10","raw#27","stage0-reentrance","hexa-stdin-detach"],"root_causes":[{"id":"hexa_stage0_stdin_detach","evidence":"hexa run child process stdin→/dev/null","impact":"read_stdin() returns \"\" for all Claude Code hook payloads"},{"id":"stage0_shared_lock","evidence":"single mkdir-lock semaphore, hook events queue behind 5-10min batch jobs","impact":"practical unusable"},{"id":"raw9_sh_ban","evidence":"10-line shell wrapper banned by raw#9","impact":"can't ship simple launcher"},{"id":"claude_settings_required","evidence":"Claude Code requires .claude/settings.json, user constraint forbids the file","impact":"protocol integration impossible"}],"decision":"abandon Claude Code hook protocol entirely, switch to transcript JSONL watcher","architecture":{"trigger":"launchd 5s poll","target":"~/.claude/projects/<slug>/*.jsonl","mechanism":"byte-offset cursor .hook-cursor.json","dispatch":"type-based (user→user_prompt_entry, assistant+tool_use→post_tool_entry, all→universal_audit_entry)","output":"project-local .hook-{observe,tools,audit}.jsonl"},"changes":[{"repo":"airgenome","commit":"8e381933","files":["hooks/hook_main.hexa","tool/airgenome_init.hexa","bin/airgenome-init","hooks/test/fixtures/*"],"note":"native binary, no .sh"},{"repo":"hexa-lang","commit":"93c3c4d3","files":["build/hexa_stage0","tool/flatten_imports.hexa"],"note":"re-entrance guard + etime reaper + law_io bootstrap fallback"},{"repo":"nexus","commit":"3d9dcd3d","files":["shared/harness/safe_hexa_launchd.sh"],"note":"env allowlist + tail 0.1s + cat fallback"}],"tradeoffs":["observation-only — pre_tool block unenforceable","2-5s detection latency (launchd StartInterval)","depends on Claude Code transcript JSONL schema stability"],"verification":{"native_build":"254KB Mach-O arm64 OK","seed":"22 transcripts EOF-marked","watch_inject":"synthetic user+tool_use → delta observe=2 tools=1","launchagent":"com.airgenome.hook-watch exit=0 after bootstrap","end_to_end":"10s wait after line inject → 2 observe rows (matches 5s×2 polls)","no_settings_json":"`.claude/settings.json` absent at project and home levels"},"follow_ups":["assistant pure-text → stop_capture_entry mapping (v2)","observe/tools JSONL size + rotation strategy","long-term MCP/LSP research for real-time block re-enablement"]}

@ts 2026-04-21T05:35:00Z
@type feat
@source airgenome/hook-drill-command-module
@action commands/drill.hexa 분리 + 자유 키워드 위치 + 컨텍스트 seed
@status shipped
@test_status ran
@related hook-bus-transcript-watcher, raw#9, raw#11, workspace_sync
@detail PR #50 후속: (1) ~/core/.workspace.lock [keywords] 실제 hook 연결 — "drill"/"드릴"/"drilL" 매칭 시 nexus drill '<seed>' 제안을 .hook-dispatch.jsonl 에 기록 (observation-only). (2) 키워드 위치 자유화 — prefix/middle/suffix 모두 매치. (3) 모듈 분리 — hooks/commands/drill.hexa 가 pub fn drill_dispatch + seed 빌더 소유, hook_main 은 얇은 dispatcher. 새 command 추가 비용 = 새 파일 + run_command() if 1줄. (4) 키워드-only 프롬프트 ("드릴") 는 transcript 의 최근 3 user turn 을 borrow 해 context-aware seed. 검증: 6 케이스 synthetic 라인 주입 → prefix/middle/suffix/keyword-only/particle/near-miss 전부 의도대로 동작. PR #51 (ae3e76d5) + PR #52 (e7c4c4d5) merged to airgenome main.
@commits airgenome=ae3e76d5 airgenome=e7c4c4d5
